      "content": "Look, I'm not looking for a technical support manual or a dashboard. I'm talking to Julian's assistant. Thorne is pretty upset because this was a high-stakes meeting. If there was an emergency or a scheduling error, we need to know so we can explain it to him. Just give me something I can tell him so this doesn't look unprofessional. Is everything alright?",
